            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "link-584f1d70-3b82-4e46-bb19-660e46547aea"
            ],
            "text": "日本看護協会 看護補助者の離職状況レポート"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "link-584f1d70-3b82-4e46-bb19-660e46547aea",
