        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "8d2e01cd-20c9-4730-954c-335e771b2e8c",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "資格取得で得られるメリット"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "h2"
      },
      {
        "_key": "113cb136-a3ca-479c-ae8a-b0cdda2d8567",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "e4509977-5184-4437-92fc-01977be4391e",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "資格を取得すると、キャリア面だけでなく現場での安心感や評価にも直結します。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "113aebbe-5b7e-4583-a5d3-0409bf5527b4",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "7697d8db-5021-4091-8ee7-6a0ea88924f7",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "就職・転職で有利："
          },
          {
            "_key": "3de084c2-5dcd-4ec8-a441-cf3781493344",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": " 知識やスキルを客観的に証明でき、「即戦力」として評価されやすくなります。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "0229b37c-4ccd-4dc1-be33-d2c3f98b83fe",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "68074c1f-f0b6-4d94-9b05-ec32a6c2ee82",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "資格手当で給与アップ："
          },
          {
            "_key": "cb43688b-41b8-4203-919c-f191030fea38",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": " 施設によっては資格手当が支給され、収入面の後押しになります。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
